# Status

Offline drift report for this gofasta project.

1. Run `gofasta status --json`.
2. Parse the `checks` array.
3. For every check where `status` is `drift` or `pending`, report the
   check name and its `detail`/`hint` field.
4. If anything is out of sync, ask the user whether to run
   `gofasta do rebuild` (Wire + Swagger) or `gofasta migrate up`
   (pending migrations) before continuing.
